Class RecommendationDto

java.lang.Object
com.FeedEmGreens.HealthyAura.dto.RecommendationDto
public class RecommendationDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing an eatery recommendation.

This DTO aggregates key eatery information, including its location, description, health/hygiene ratings, and dynamically generated recommendation data such as proximity, reason, and overall score.

It is primarily used by the recommendation engine in RecManager and served via the homeController endpoints.

Example JSON response:

{
  "id": 12,
  "name": "GreenBite",
  "address": "123 Orchard Road",
  "fullAddress": "123 Orchard Road, Singapore 238888",
  "tags": ["Vegan", "Budget-Friendly"],
  "description": "Healthy and affordable meals",
  "longitude": 103.832,
  "latitude": 1.303,
  "distance": 0.8,
  "reason": "Close by â€¢ Vegan option",
  "score": 92.5,
  "averageHealth": 4.6,
  "averageHygiene": 4.7,
  "reviewCount": 45
}
